    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the making of holes in metal, wood, or other materials, and for making holes in the earth, as for drilling a well or for oil.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
